Replace process_template_pipeline_one(ss, job_conf) with your function Example: process_alerts(ss, job_conf)
 
0.8 — Add GitHub Actions Workflow File
If not already present from the fork:
• Check: .github/workflows/ci.yml exists in your repo
• If missing: Copy ci.yml from the python-etl-template repo (.github/workflows/) into your repo
⚠️ Note: In Helios 1.0 repos, rename helios-config.yml to helios-config.yml.bak to stop old deployment and use GitHub Actions instead.
 
