Step 4.3 — Raise Pull Request: dev → staging
• In GitHub, open a PR from: your dev branch → staging branch
• Add meaningful title and description of changes
• Assign reviewers for approval
• Once approved and merged, GitHub Actions auto-deploys to Prod-Pilot environment
 
Step 4.4 — Verify in Airflow PRE-PROD
• Access Airflow Prod-Pilot and verify your DAG appears
